headline: Assessing Archer-Daniels-Midland (ADM) Stock’s Valuation After Its Strong Year-to-Date Share Price Gain
summary: Archer-Daniels-Midland (ADM) has quietly outperformed this year, with the stock up about 18% year to date and roughly 19% over the past year, even after a recent pullback. See our latest analysis for Archer-Daniels-Midland. That recent 1 month share price return of 4.8% looks more like a reset than a breakout, but it still caps an impressive year to date run as investors reassess Archer-Daniels-Midland's earnings resilience and risk profile.
